meaning_str.bing:
v. 旅行；旅游；传播；流传
n. 旅行；泛指出行；游历；尤指一系列的经常性出行
网络. 行程；游记

旅行；泛指出行；游历；尤指一系列的经常性出行

旅游；旅行；游历；（以某速度、朝某方向或在某距离内）行进；移动；（光、声等）传播；（球等）滚动；遍及；巡回；经过；穿越；巡回；经过；穿越；（消息、作品等）流传；盛行各地
旅游；旅行；行程；差旅；移动；行进；传播；运动范围；活动范围

1.en: During the Civil War, the Shenandoah Valley was a strategic area, as it was on the main travel route north and south.
1.cn: 内战时期，谢南多厄河谷（ShenandoahValley）是一个战略上的重要地区，因为它位在南北主要通道上。

2.en: On Hainan Island, travel agent Ou has no doubt who will emerge the winner among China and its neighbors.
2.cn: 毫无疑问，海南岛的旅行代理商欧小姐将在冬天出现在中国及其邻国。

3.en: The route is still to be announced but the Indian media has reported that the torch will travel less than a third of the original 9km route.
3.cn: 在印度的奥运火炬传递具体路线仍有待公布，但据印度媒体报道，奥运火炬在新德里的传递行程，将不到其原定9公里路线的三分之一。

0.en: And how is it you have means to travel?

1.en: No! We've done our ocean travels. That part of our lives is over. The only reason to travel in the first place is so you don't have to travel ever again. Yeah, but I want to...
1.cn: 不!我们不做海洋旅行了.那种日子结束了.旅行唯一的理由就是——以后再也不必旅行了。对，但我想……

2.en: Oh, yeah, sure, let me just put this in a travel mug.
2.cn: 好，当然，等我把咖啡倒旅行杯里。

3.en: Our butler takes care of me at home, but when I travel I usually fend for myself.
3.cn: 在家男管家会照顾我，但我旅行时就得自己打点了。

4.en: Ladies and gentlemen, I have achieved time travel. Thank you. I am farkle!
4.cn: 女士们先生们，这是场时光旅行，谢谢大家，我是法尔科！

5.en: We are what you might call progressive. I hear you're interested in space travel.
5.cn: 你可以称我们是进取者，我听说你对太空旅行很感兴趣。

6.en: But the warping of space-time may also provide shortcuts that could make interstellar travel a snap.
6.cn: 但时空的弯曲也许也提供了可以使星际旅行瞬间实现的捷径。

7.en: Mostly, men stay in their village far from the dark of the Jungle. But sometimes they travel.
7.cn: 人类生活的村子里，他们远离森林的黑暗，但有些时候他们会旅行。

8.en: Air travel, more than any other mode of modern transportation, has bridged our continent and sped up our lives. And every year, more and more of us are taking to the skies.
8.cn: 航空旅行，对比其他任何现代交通模式，让我们在大陆间更快捷的穿梭每年，我们都有更多的人 选择空中旅行。

9.en: I can't travel with you. I don't keep you warm at night. I don't see you the way he sees you.
9.cn: 我不能和你一起旅行，不能在夜里让你感到温暖，也不能像他那样看待你。

10.en: Yes! You know, in six months, the statute of limitations runs out and I can travel internationally again.
10.cn: 当然了！再过6个月我的禁令就过期了。到时候我又可以作国际旅行了。

11.en: And for nearly 100 years, America's railways were the fastest and most popular way to travel, but not anymore.
11.cn: 将近100年来，美国的铁路都是最快最流行的旅行方式，不过再也不是了。

12.en: They have another 10 months on their trip home. Space travel is dangerous, they need to be alert and undistracted.
12.cn: 他们还有10个月的航程回家，太空旅行很危险，他们需要警觉且不能分心。

13.en: I loved travel, but there're something I really miss when I'm away. What, Daddy? My darlings, of course.
13.cn: 虽然我热爱旅行，但在我离家的日子里很想念一样东西。什么东西？当然是我亲爱的家人了！

14.en: Space travel has been a staple of the movies from the very beginning, but the feature film Interstellar has a unique pedigree.
14.cn: 从最开始，太空旅行就成为电影的主题但故事片《星际穿越》有独特的背景。

15.en: I love to travel. But that something I really miss when I'm away. What, Daddy? My darlings, of course.
15.cn: 哎，虽然我热爱旅行。但在我离家的日子里很想念一样东西。什么东西？当然是我亲爱的家人了！哈哈哈。

16.en: Air travel is so common today that our airways are filled with all kinds of travelers , some of them more unusual than others.
16.cn: 空中旅行变得如此普通了，我们的航空路线到处都是旅行者，其中有那么一些不寻常的。

17.en: Why don't we all just settle down for a minute. Look, it's gotten late. Too late to travel. So, why don't we all just have a little honey.
17.cn: 现在天都晚了，大家先静一静。看，天色已晚，旅行没戏了，要不咱们来点蜂蜜尝尝。

18.en: The chronosphere. The source that powers the grand clock of all time. Legend has, it also lets one travel across the ocean of time.
18.cn: 超时空魔球，据说它就是驱动世界上所有时间的动力源泉，传说通过它还能穿越古今，回到过去，进行时间旅行。

19.en: New travel measures are now directing all travelers from the three affected countries in West Africa into five U.S. airports where we're conducting additional screening.
19.cn: 新的旅行措施正在指引着所有来自西非三个疫区国家的旅客从美国的五个机场入关，在这五个机场我们正在实施着额外的筛查措施。
